    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Idle是初始状态。遇到普通非文档行就保持Idle；遇到## directive指令就进入CollectingDocs收集状态。另外还要处理CategorySet和FileDoc两个分支状态。",
